title: Embarrassment
content:
I was having so much fun with this and got carried away and forgot about the deadline. (I finished on Friday night, and thought wanted to send it the next day...heck)

I thought I don't want to waste it and decided to risk public embarrassment by posting them here.

Feel free to comment... (and kill me if you want to...)
